1.2 (30-Jun-2012)
	- Fixed the plugin not working in L4D1.

1.1 (22-Jun-2012)
	- Added cvar "l4d_molotov_shove_timed" to control which infected use the following cvar.
	- Added cvar "l4d_molotov_shove_timeout" to set how long infected will burn for.

1.0 (20-Jun-2012)
	- Initial release.

======================================================================================*/

